abstract: Kentucky is No 1 in AP Top 25 college basketball teams.
lead_paragraph: Kentucky was No. 1 in the A.P. Top 25, but no longer unanimously, after two overtime wins. The Wildcats (15-0) were atop 63 of 65 ballots.
